9. **`highScoresTable.appendChild(tableHeader)`**: The table header is appended to the table.  
10. **`const tableBody = document.createElement("tbody")`**: A table body is created.  
11. **`for (let i = 0; i < highScores.length; i++)`**: A loop is used to iterate through each high score.  
12. **`const row = document.createElement("tr")`**: A table row is created for each high score.  
13. **`row.innerHTML = \`<td>\${i + 1}</td><td>\${highScores[i].name}</td><td>\${highScores[i].score}</td>\`**  
